      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus derived from five tensile coupons machined from the same bar stock as the test screws. Geometry measured by CMM with 5 µm accuracy. Monte Carlo propagation of material and geometric uncertainty shows QoI coefficient of variation <3%, confirming input uncertainty is not dominant."
