      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 standard loading configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated; the clinical use envelope includes varied angulation and load rates not captured here. Required level 3 not achieved; this factor is flagged as below required level. Risk accepted given conservative nature of F1717 protocol relative to in vivo loading."
