      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9: stiffness E/uval=0.82, yield force E/uval=1.14, force at 40 mm E/uval=1.31. Percentage differences: stiffness 4.2%, yield force 6.8%, force at 40 mm 5.1%. All metrics within acceptance bounds across both laboratories. Output comparison criterion satisfied."
