      "rationale": "Construct stiffness governs load transfer to adjacent vertebrae; yield force determines onset of permanent deformation; force at 40 mm displacement characterizes post-yield reserve. All three QoIs are explicitly required by FDA guidance for 510(k) submissions referencing ASTM F1717. Relevance to COU confirmed."
