    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single test condition; risk accepted given the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the medium model risk level. Quantitative output comparison metrics (E/uval <1.96, percentage difference <10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across both independent laboratories. Overall credibility sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
